The paper discusses logical characterization of bisimulation in labelled Markov processes, which is a topic related to logic and formal methods. Therefore, cs.LO (Logic in Computer Science) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also involves concepts from information theory (cs.IT), discrete mathematics (cs.DM), programming languages (cs.PL), and machine learning (cs.LG).
